headline.main: Fueling Up for a Long Campaign: Hillary Clinton Lunches at Chipotle

snippet: Driving to Iowa for her first campaign swing on Monday, Hillary Rodham Clinton stopped for lunch at a Chipotle in Maumee, Ohio, outside Toledo.
